=head1 NAME

t/stm/basic.t -- Single-threaded tests of the STM opcodes and PMC types.

=head1 SYNOPSIS

    % prove t/stm/basic.t

=head1 DESCRIPTION

Makes sure the STM opcodes and the STMVar and STMRef PMC types work as expected
in easy, single-threaded cases.

=cut

